These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, 7up, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, surfing, rugby, baseball
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | tea         | hot-chocolate   | 7up | coffee       |
| Sport      | baseball | swimming | rugby   | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, writing, rock-climbing, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, polish, indian, italian
1. the italian is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the polish##2
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
3. the indian is on the right of the thai##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | writing | woodworking | rock-climbing | photography |
| Nationality   | polish    | italian   | thai | indian       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, garlic, strawberry, avocado
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, indian, italian, russian
1. the italian is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
2. the italian is between the indian and the person eating garlic##2
3. the indian is on the far left##1
4. the russian is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person eating garlic is the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | avocado    | orange | garlic   | strawberry  |
| Nationality   | indian | italian   | russian | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, goat, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, sailing, volleyball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the person who's sport is baseball and the owner of the hamster##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | hamster   | bird    | goat       | frog   |
| Sport   | volleyball | cricket | baseball | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up, sprite, lemonade
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, photography, puzzles, collecting
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | almond-milk        | sprite | lemonade  | 7up |
| Hobby      | puzzles | photography  | collecting | reading    |

