.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, rock, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, biathlon, snowboarding, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
4. the fan of house is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the fan of rock is between the fan of ambient and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | house     | rock           | ambient | trance  |
| Sport         | lacrosse | ice-hockey | biathlon   | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, techno, pop, jazz
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, car, van, tram
1. the fan of techno is the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the fan of classical is between the person driving the jet-ski and the fan of pop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | techno | classical | pop      |
| Transport     | van | jet-ski    | car  | tram |

