.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, volleyball, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, skateboard, subway
1. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person driving the skateboard##2
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | climbing | skiing | volleyball     | golf   |
| Transport   | skateboard   | bike     | subway | airplane |

