.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, musician, firefighter, engineer
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, roller, skateboard
1. the firefighter is between the person driving the snowmobile and the journalist##2
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the journalist##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the journalist is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | musician | firefighter | journalist | engineer |
| Transport   | snowmobile         | skateboard       | subway    | roller         |

