.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, orange, tomato, grapes
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, parkour, handball, golf
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
3. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating orange##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person eating orange and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | grapes   | tomato      | orange   | banana  |
| Sport   | golf | parkour | handball | snowboarding |

