.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, plum, grapes, watermelon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, thriller, martial-arts, documentary
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person eating plum is between the person eating watermelon and the person eating apricot##2
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | apricot     | plum | watermelon   | grapes        |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | martial-arts   | thriller | documentary |

