.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, camping, skydiving, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, disco, country, techno
1. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of funk is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the fan of disco##1
5. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the fan of disco is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is video-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping | skydiving | video-games | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | country          | disco     | techno  | funk     |

