2. the social-worker is between the person watching disaster movies and the scientist##2
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | scientist | social-worker | teacher | freelancer     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | spy    | disaster   | zombie |

