.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, italian, argentine, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, tram, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the brazilian is the person driving the tram##1
3. the argentine is between the person driving the tram and the italian##2
4. the brazilian is on the right of the argentine##1
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | italian | argentine | brazilian |
| Transport     | car     | jet-ski   | quad-bike | tram  |

