.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indian, australian, dutch
4 different pets are kept: horse, fish, ferret, bird
1. the argentine is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the dutch is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the horse and the indian##2
4. the owner of the bird is the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | dutch | indian | argentine | australian |
| Pet           | ferret  | bird  | fish | horse      |

