.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish, canadian, dutch
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, surfing, cycling, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the dutch is the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the malaysian and the canadian##2
5. the canadian is the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | dutch   | malaysian   | turkish | canadian |
| Sport         | tennis | surfing | skateboarding     | cycling    |

