.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, traveling, photography, reading
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, lizard, turtle
1. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the owner of the goldfish and the person who's hobby is reading##2
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | photography    | reading     | fishing | traveling |
| Pet     | rat | turtle | lizard       | goldfish     |

 